<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>데뷔 시나리오 테스트 : 당신의 연습생 유형은?</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --pd-pink: #ff78bb;
            --pd-blue: #72d2ff;
            --pd-dark-blue: #1a2a6c;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Pretendard', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--pd-blue) 0%, var(--pd-pink) 100%);
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #333;
        }

        #game-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 500px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hidden { display: none; }

        h2 { color: var(--pd-dark-blue); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: keep-all; min-height: 3em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        
        .option-btn {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 12px 0;
            border: 2px solid var(--pd-blue);
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            text-align: left;
            word-break: keep-all;
        }
        .option-btn:hover {
            background: var(--pd-blue);
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        #progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 10px;
            background: #eee;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        #progress-inner {
            height: 100%;
            width: 0%;
            background: var(--pd-pink);
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }

        #result-title { font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--pd-pink); font-weight: 800; margin: 15px 0; }
        #result-desc { line-height: 1.7; text-align: left; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem; background: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; }
        
        /* 이스터에그를 위한 스타일 추가 */
        #main-title {
            cursor: pointer;
            user-select: none;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
        }

        .start-btn {
            background: var(--pd-pink);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 18px 50px;
            border-radius: 35px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 120, 187, 0.4);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="game-container">
    <div id="start-page">
        <h1 id="main-title" onclick="triggerEgg()" style="color: var(--pd-dark-blue); letter-spacing: 2px;">PICK ME!</h1>
        <p style="font-weight: 600;">만약 당신이 서바이벌 프로그램에 출연한다면?</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 30px;">19가지 질문으로 분석하는 당신의 '데뷔 시나리오'</p>
        <button class="start-btn" onclick="startTest()">테스트 시작하기</button>
    </div>

    <div id="quiz-page" class="hidden">
        <div id="progress-bar"><div id="progress-inner"></div></div>
        <div id="question-text"></div>
        <div id="options-container"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="result-page" class="hidden">
        <div style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888;">당신의 데뷔 시나리오는</div>
        <div id="result-title"></div>
        <div id="result-desc"></div>
        <button class="option-btn" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 25px; background: var(--pd-dark-blue); color: white; border: none;" onclick="location.reload()">다시 테스트하기</button>
    </div>
</div>

<script>
